events.description:
It’s that time of the year - @718sessions returns May 24 for their season opening in The Ruins.

@dannykrivit - one of dance musics most foundational DJ’s - holds court in The Ruins as only he can. Krivit is joined by longtime collaborator @bennysoto, an essential force behind the long-running 718 Sessions. 

Tickets now available on DICE, link in bio.
